    public interface OOPAnnotator
extends edu.stanford.nlp.pipeline.Annotator

    Interface for all custom annotators.

    Extends the corenlp annotator interface.

    Implementations must be re-entrant.

    Instances will be used by Analyzer as follows:

    OOPAnnotator oopAnnotator = new Annotator(); oopAnnotator.init(parameterStore); oopAnnotator.annotate(coreDocument); oopAnnotator.serialize(coreDocument, json); oopAnnotator.serializeAggregateDocument(coreDocument, json); oopAnnotator.getAnnotationClass(); oopAnnotator.getDescription();
    Author:
    Ram Sadasiv
    See Also:
    AbstractAnnotator
